YWriteToParcel - Annotation Type in br.org.yacamim.entity
This annotation class is meant to be use when it's necessary to sign to Yacamim that an field (that is accessed from a getter) of a BaseEntity subclass will not be persisted when the class it's member of will be "parceled" (serialized).
